<%= pageHeading "Getting Started for Students" %>

<p>Welcome to <%= SITE_NAME %>! This help page will guide you through creating an account, registering for a class and completing assignments in OST. 
  Click on the below links to learn more about each help topic. Be sure to check out our <%= link_to "video tutorials", help_student_tutorials_path %>, too.</p>

  <p>As always, feel free to <%= email_link "support", "email our friendly support team" %> if you 
  need one-on-one help.</p>

